headers.subject: [tosdr:2114] [neutral] Tumblr does store token regarding your financial info

html:
We do receive certain information from our Payment Processor: (1) a unique token that we connect with your Account to enable you to make further purchases using the information stored by our Payment Processor and (2) in certain cases, the last four digits of the credit card number associated with that token, so that we can prevent fraudulent transactions and identity theft.

http://www.tumblr.com/policy/en/privacy
